# .i18n-glossary — TKX Git Release Pipeline term mappings (v0.9.12 Sprint A)
#
# Consumed by scripts/glossary-loader.sh, injected as few-shot prompt prefix
# into translate-file.sh's LLM call to enforce term consistency across all
# translated docs.
#
# format: <zh>|<en>|<context/note (optional)>
# Comments start with #; blank lines OK.
# [NO_TRANSLATE] section lists glob patterns / literal tokens to preserve verbatim.

# ── Core release pipeline terms ─────────────────────────────────────────
发版|release|verb action; prefer over "publish" in release.sh context
打包|packaging|noun: the act; for noun "package" use 包
脱敏|sanitize|verb; scanning for secrets/PII
平摊|flatten|verb; spreading docs into Release dir
审计|audit|both noun and verb (per release-audit.sh)
回归|regression|test regression / change-detection sense
门控|gate|policy gate / pre-push gate
软警告|soft warning|warn() in audit, vs check() FAIL
硬阻断|hard block|abort with non-zero exit
版本|version|
签名|signing|GPG/sigstore signing
契约|contract|interface contract (e.g. install.sh §6.10)
幂等|idempotent|same input → same output regardless of run count
可复现|reproducible|byte-identical builds

# ── Skill / Claude Code ecosystem terms ─────────────────────────────────
技能|skill|Claude Code skill (file at SKILL.md)
触发词|trigger keyword|frontmatter description tokens
上下文|context|context window
基线|baseline|always-loaded portion (e.g. SKILL.md)
按需加载|on-demand load|references/* loaded when SKILL.md instructs

# ── TKX policy terms ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
政策|policy|TKX_Git_Release_policy_and_process.md
条款|clause|policy clause (e.g. §10.10)

# ── NO_TRANSLATE — preserve these verbatim ──────────────────────────────
